name: Uint16Array.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 2 in the case of Uint16Array.

name: Uint16Array.prototype.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 2 in the case of a Uint16Array.

name: Uint16Array.prototype.constructor
description: The constructor function that created the instance object. For Uint16Array instances, the initial value is the Uint16Array constructor.
